           Delegated      6.535M (± 1.6%) i/s -     33.147M in   5.073785s

Comparison:
             Defined: 13608493.7 i/s
             Wrapped: 13194426.2 i/s - same-ish: difference falls within error
           Delegated:  6534500.5 i/s - 2.08x  slower
